Package oracle.apps.fnd.appltest.diagfwk.api Description

Provides the core interfaces that the test authors would depend on when creating Java diagnostic tests.

Package Specification

Provides the following interfaces.

  • DiagTest - A Java interface that models a diagnostic test.
  • AbstractDiagTest - An abstract base class that implements the DiagTest interface. Test authors are strongly recommended to extend their test classes from this base class.
  • DiagContext - A context object that is passed to a diagnostic test during execution. The context provides handlers to the report related objects as well as input and output parameters for the test.
